  <brief_title>Study to Compare CAUTI Rates Following ERASE CAUTI Tray Non-Silver vs Silver Coated Foley Catheters</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Clinical Study to Compare the CAUTI Rates Following ERASE CAUTI Tray Non-Silver Coated Foley Catheters Verse Silver Coated Foley Catheters</official_title>
  <sponsors>
